How This Helps Structure a Django Book

Example structure:

Part 1 — Foundations
Part 2 — Core Concepts
Part 3 — Building Applications
Part 4 — APIs
Part 5 — Debugging & Best Practices
Part 6 — Deployment
Part 7 — Advanced Django

This approach makes the book feel like a guided learning journey instead of scattered tutorials.
